South African Union Agrees Wage Deal With African Rainbow’s Nkomati Nickel

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-05T13:11:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-05/south-african-union-agrees-wage-deal-with-african-rainbow-s-nkomati-nickel.html
South Africa ’s National Union of
Mineworkers said it agreed a one-year deal with Nkomati Nickel
Mine, a unit of  African Rainbow Minerals Ltd. (ARI)  that will see
wages increase by between 9 percent and 10 percent depending on
the pay grade.  “This agreement was concluded after a six-day  strike
action  which ended yesterday,” the labor union said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  